<l>oṇṇutaṟ kōo vuṭaintatē ñāṭpiṉuḷ</l>
<l> naṇṇārum muṭkumeṉ pīṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>On her bright brow alone is destroyed even that power of mine that used to terrify the most fearless foes in the battlefield.</l>
